                <p>
               <pb/>
               <hi rend="italic">Emigration.</hi> –The <hi rend="italic">Venus</hi>  steam-boar left the Steam <lb/>Packet Wharf, St Katherine's Dock, yesterday morn<lb break="no"/>ing, with from 230 to 240 female emigrants to take <lb/>their passage on board the ship Canton, for Sydney. <lb/>The emigrants were, for the most part, fine healthy <lb/>looking girls, some of them of exceedingly interesting <lb/>appearance, and almost all of a class much above that <lb/>in which the distress which prompts to emigration <lb/>would be supposed to exist.</p>
            </body>
