                <p>
               <pb/>A new principle has been recognised in the regula<lb break="no"/>tions attendant upon the transportation of convicts <lb/>from this country to New South Wales. Boys of six <lb/>and girls of ten years will be allowed to accompany <lb/>their parents to that distant colony.</p>
